summary: In Endgame i was just thinking what if bucky dies and then i cried and then i thought of a really sad line . . steve: bucky, no,...
body:
In Endgame

i was just thinking what if bucky dies

and then i cried

and then i thought of a really sad line

.

.

steve: bucky, no, no, you can’t—

bucky: hey, steve, don’t cry, we made it.

steve: no, you have to make it—

bucky: *smiles sadly* steve, we made it, we made it to the end of the line.

bucky: *hand squeeze*

bucky: *dies*

.

.

I’m crying so much ahahaha

if ANYONE DIES I WILL CRY :(


( Masterlist )

summary: I feel like marvel comics (and probably DC too) could save the industry with a single website. Like make a site that has some...
body: I feel like marvel comics (and probably DC too) could save the industry with a single website. Like make a site that has some good “starter” comics, ones that don’t require any background knowledge. Then have a function where users can input comics they’ve read/enjoyed and it will suggest new ones with the same character/characters, similar writing, or others from that arc. If they would just stop making it so impossible to get started or to find new stuff for anyone who isnt a superfan with tons of background knowledge already.
